---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="住客分享 - 夏洛克Villa民宿">
  <div class="blog-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="header-section">
        <h6 class="section-subtitle">GUEST STORIES</h6>
        <h1>住客分享</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">聽聽旅客們的夏洛克體驗</p>
      </div>

      <div class="blog-grid">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">
            <img src="/lake-view.png" alt="湖畔時光" />
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span class="blog-date">2024-11-15</span>
              <span class="blog-category">家庭旅遊</span>
            </div>
            <h3>寧靜的湖畔時光</h3>
            <p>
              帶著家人來到夏洛克，孩子們在湖邊餵魚、在泳池戲水，大人則在庭園裡悠閒散步。遠離都市的喧囂，這裡真的是放鬆身心的好地方。
            </p>
            <div class="blog-author">
              <span>— 王小姐 from 台北</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">
            <img src="/manor-exterior.png" alt="莊園建築" />
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span class="blog-date">2024-10-28</span>
              <span class="blog-category">情侶出遊</span>
            </div>
            <h3>浪漫的莊園假期</h3>
            <p>
              和另一半來這裡度過週末，莊園的環境讓人驚艷。清晨在湖邊散步，傍晚在庭園看夕陽，每一刻都很美好。房間也很舒適，下次還想再來。
            </p>
            <div class="blog-author">
              <span>— 李先生 from 新竹</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">
            <img src="/swimming-pool.png" alt="泳池樂趣" />
          </div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span class="blog-date">2024-10-10</span>
              <span class="blog-category">朋友聚會</span>
            </div>
            <h3>久違的朋友聚會</h3>
            <p>
              選擇夏洛克作為朋友聚會地點真是太對了！寬敞的空間讓我們可以盡情聊天，泳池、湖泊都很適合拍照。管家服務也很貼心，讓我們玩得很開心。
            </p>
            <div class="blog-author">
              <span>— 陳小姐 from 台中</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>想分享您的夏洛克體驗嗎？</h2>
        <p>歡迎在 Facebook 或 Instagram 標註我們，分享您的美好回憶！</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/summerrocker2014"
            target="_blank"
            class="cta-btn primary"
          >
            Facebook
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://booking.owlting.com/summerrockvilla"
            target="_blank"
            class="cta-btn secondary"
          >
            立即訂房
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .blog-container {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .blog-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-bg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(138, 163, 135, 0.15);
    border-color: var(--resort-light);
  }

  .blog-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 220px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .blog-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .blog-card:hover .blog-image img {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .blog-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .blog-date,
  .blog-category {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--resort-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .blog-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .blog-content p {
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .blog-author {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .cta-btn.primary {
    background: var(--resort-primary);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .cta-btn.primary:hover {
    background: var(--resort-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(138, 163, 135, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-btn.secondary {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--resort-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--resort-primary);
  }

  .cta-btn.secondary:hover {
    background: var(--resort-pale);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-container {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .blog-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
